---
title: "The Boatmen of Barisal: A Vanishing Song"
category: cultural
excerpt: How the Bhatiali river songs are disappearing — and why we're recording them before they're gone.
featured: true
read_time: 8 min read
---
The river does not judge. It only carries. In the heart of Barisal, where the water is the only road, the sound of the 'Bhatiali' songs once filled the dusk. Today, these songs are fading.
